00:00:08.776 --> 00:00:10.678 position:30% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] Here.
A lock of Lord Claude's hair.

00:00:10.812 --> 00:00:11.813 position:27% line:89% align:start
Treasure it well.

00:00:11.946 --> 00:00:13.347 position:33% line:89% align:start
Lord Claude?

00:00:13.480 --> 00:00:16.149 position:19% line:83% align:start
What joy it is to hold
even a small piece of you!

00:00:16.283 --> 00:00:18.452 position:38% line:83% align:start
[ALMOND]
All hail! All hail!

00:00:18.586 --> 00:00:19.954 position:33% line:89% align:start
[chattering]

00:00:20.087 --> 00:00:21.255 position:35% line:83% align:start
[BELZEBUTH]
He's here!

00:00:21.388 --> 00:00:23.357 position:24% line:83% align:start
Through this measly
scrap of hair.

00:00:24.424 --> 00:00:26.093 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm not concerned, Isaac.

00:00:26.226 --> 00:00:27.795 position:5% line:89% align:start
This version of Lord Claude is--

00:00:27.929 --> 00:00:31.298 position:13% line:83% align:start
Let's just say with a good
scheme, it'll be smooth sailing.

00:00:31.431 --> 00:00:33.367 position:21% line:83% align:start
Goodness. You should
really use a gentler touch

00:00:33.501 --> 00:00:35.537 position:27% line:83% align:start
when dealing with
the demon lord!

00:00:35.670 --> 00:00:38.138 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'll do whatever it takes
to save our engagement!

00:00:38.272 --> 00:00:40.274 position:19% line:83% align:start
And trust me, I'll be
very gentle and loving

00:00:40.407 --> 00:00:41.743 position:21% line:89% align:start
once he can't escape.

00:00:41.876 --> 00:00:44.612 position:19% line:83% align:start
But first, I must have
him under my thumb.

00:00:44.746 --> 00:00:46.681 position:27% line:83% align:start
If I were in that
poor man's shoes,

00:00:46.814 --> 00:00:48.750 position:24% line:83% align:start
it'd feel more akin
to falling off a cliff

00:00:48.883 --> 00:00:49.918 position:33% line:89% align:start
than in love.

00:00:50.050 --> 00:00:51.385 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's right!

00:00:51.519 --> 00:00:52.620 position:24% line:83% align:start
And yours truly will
give him a hardy push

00:00:52.754 --> 00:00:53.788 position:33% line:89% align:start
off the edge!

00:00:53.922 --> 00:00:55.255 position:13% line:89% align:start
Into the abyss of my love!

00:00:55.389 --> 00:00:57.291 position:19% line:83% align:start
And then build a fence
around it so it's so high

00:00:57.424 --> 00:00:58.793 position:24% line:89% align:start
he can't climb out!

00:02:29.182 --> 00:02:31.284 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
An inspection of the kingdom?

00:02:31.418 --> 00:02:32.820 position:38% line:83% align:start
[JASPER]
Yeah. How peculiar.

00:02:32.954 --> 00:02:35.089 position:21% line:83% align:start
Has the news not been
released that the demon lord

00:02:35.222 --> 00:02:37.290 position:27% line:83% align:start
has lost both his
memories and his powers?

00:02:37.424 --> 00:02:39.627 position:13% line:83% align:start
[JASPER] It has; that's why
he's doing all this.

00:02:39.761 --> 00:02:42.496 position:21% line:83% align:start
An "inspection" puts
him back out there.

00:02:42.630 --> 00:02:44.666 position:21% line:83% align:start
CÃ©dric and Lilia are
tagging along to boost

00:02:44.799 --> 00:02:46.067 position:30% line:89% align:start
public opinion.

00:02:46.199 --> 00:02:47.869 position:19% line:89% align:start
Interesting selection.

00:02:48.002 --> 00:02:50.170 position:16% line:83% align:start
Sure, but it makes sense
because I hear it was

00:02:50.303 --> 00:02:52.140 position:19% line:83% align:start
Lady Lilia who thought
up and organized

00:02:52.272 --> 00:02:53.708 position:24% line:89% align:start
this whole ordeal.

00:02:53.841 --> 00:02:57.344 position:24% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] Of course,
she was the one behind this.

00:02:57.477 --> 00:02:59.614 position:21% line:83% align:start
[LILIA] This world is
only a game, silly.

00:03:00.715 --> 00:03:02.150 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] There's a decent
chance this sets up another

00:03:02.282 --> 00:03:05.153 position:13% line:89% align:start
turning point in the game.

00:03:05.285 --> 00:03:08.422 position:16% line:83% align:start
Elephas. What would you do
to coax Lord Claude's poor,

00:03:08.556 --> 00:03:11.926 position:10% line:83% align:start
clouded mind into remembering
his past, pray tell?

00:03:12.060 --> 00:03:13.561 position:21% line:89% align:start
Nothing too complex.

00:03:13.695 --> 00:03:16.130 position:21% line:83% align:start
I would expose him to
memorable things from his past.

00:03:16.263 --> 00:03:17.932 position:16% line:89% align:start
That might do the trick.

00:03:18.066 --> 00:03:21.102 position:19% line:83% align:start
Well, his exposure to me
didn't do a single thing.

00:03:21.234 --> 00:03:23.738 position:13% line:89% align:start
Oh, boo. I'm not memorable.

00:03:23.871 --> 00:03:25.073 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't despair, Miss.

00:03:25.205 --> 00:03:26.808 position:16% line:89% align:start
I doubt that's the issue.

00:03:26.941 --> 00:03:29.877 position:19% line:83% align:start
The power you hold and
his memories are at odds.

00:03:30.011 --> 00:03:32.680 position:19% line:83% align:start
You can't overlook the
holy sword you wield.

00:03:32.814 --> 00:03:35.917 position:10% line:83% align:start
You're saying the power from
the sword has something

00:03:36.050 --> 00:03:36.951 position:30% line:89% align:start
to do with it?

00:03:37.085 --> 00:03:38.251 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:03:38.385 --> 00:03:40.420 position:19% line:83% align:start
His magic and memories
are intertwined,

00:03:40.555 --> 00:03:43.290 position:5% line:89% align:start
and the sword trumps his magic.

00:03:43.423 --> 00:03:45.026 position:19% line:83% align:start
Interacting with demons
that have magic

00:03:45.159 --> 00:03:48.328 position:19% line:83% align:start
more similar to his own
might stimulate his memory.

00:03:48.462 --> 00:03:49.864 position:35% line:89% align:start
Good idea.

00:03:49.997 --> 00:03:52.900 position:16% line:83% align:start
My love has always had a
close bond with his demons.

00:03:53.034 --> 00:03:54.401 position:16% line:89% align:start
On the subject of demons,

00:03:54.535 --> 00:03:56.403 position:13% line:83% align:start
people have been notifying
the paper en masse

00:03:56.537 --> 00:03:58.539 position:10% line:89% align:start
about sightings around town.

00:03:58.673 --> 00:04:00.373 position:21% line:83% align:start
The darlings must've
abandoned the forest

00:04:00.508 --> 00:04:02.844 position:13% line:89% align:start
to search for Lord Claude.

00:04:02.977 --> 00:04:04.377 position:24% line:89% align:start
What a coincidence.

00:04:04.512 --> 00:04:05.980 position:10% line:83% align:start
Could this little inspection
have something to do

00:04:06.114 --> 00:04:07.347 position:27% line:89% align:start
with the demons?

00:04:08.883 --> 00:04:10.918 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh. Here you are.

00:04:11.052 --> 00:04:12.153 position:24% line:89% align:start
This is from Denis.

00:04:12.285 --> 00:04:13.788 position:16% line:89% align:start
He says it's a blueprint.

00:04:13.921 --> 00:04:15.556 position:24% line:89% align:start
Perfect. Thank you.

00:04:15.690 --> 00:04:18.526 position:27% line:83% align:start
Explain. What are
the blueprints for?

00:04:18.659 --> 00:04:20.728 position:35% line:83% align:start
Just a few
preparations to be safe.

00:04:20.862 --> 00:04:23.931 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well? Care to fill me in
on your next scheme?

00:04:24.065 --> 00:04:25.199 position:30% line:89% align:start
With pleasure.

00:04:25.332 --> 00:04:27.935 position:21% line:83% align:start
I mean to infiltrate
this inspection!

00:04:28.736 --> 00:04:30.171 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Listen, darling.

00:04:30.303 --> 00:04:31.806 position:21% line:83% align:start
If you see me out and
about during the inspection

00:04:31.939 --> 00:04:34.242 position:21% line:83% align:start
next week, be sure to
cover for me, okay?

00:04:34.374 --> 00:04:35.676 position:30% line:89% align:start
What? But why?

00:04:35.810 --> 00:04:37.712 position:27% line:83% align:start
You expect me to
protect an intruder?

00:04:37.845 --> 00:04:39.312 position:13% line:89% align:start
How dare you barge in here!

00:04:39.446 --> 00:04:41.582 position:5% line:89% align:start
Ah! It's been three whole days!

00:04:41.716 --> 00:04:43.851 position:41% line:83% align:start
Please!
Just who do you think you are?

00:04:43.985 --> 00:04:46.286 position:30% line:83% align:start
That's simple--
I'm your fiancÃ©e!

00:04:46.419 --> 00:04:48.656 position:27% line:89% align:start
Only temporarily.

00:04:48.790 --> 00:04:51.458 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'll have to make it so that I
am to your body like water,

00:04:51.592 --> 00:04:54.028 position:16% line:83% align:start
and you'll slowly wither
away without me.

00:05:03.604 --> 00:05:04.972 position:24% line:89% align:start
I brought a treat!

00:05:05.106 --> 00:05:07.575 position:19% line:83% align:start
An apple pie baked with
the utmost care and love!

00:05:07.708 --> 00:05:09.744 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
No, thank you.

00:05:09.877 --> 00:05:11.512 position:13% line:89% align:start
What's that you're reading?

00:05:11.646 --> 00:05:14.649 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hardly any of your concern.

00:05:14.782 --> 00:05:16.083 position:19% line:89% align:start
This is fun, isn't it?

00:05:16.217 --> 00:05:19.887 position:21% line:83% align:start
"Fun" isn't anywhere
near the word I'd use.

00:05:20.021 --> 00:05:22.690 position:19% line:83% align:start
Do you know, I've never
experienced unrequited

00:05:22.824 --> 00:05:25.226 position:33% line:83% align:start
love before.
I find it a bit thrilling.

00:05:25.358 --> 00:05:26.694 position:35% line:89% align:start
[knocking]

00:05:26.828 --> 00:05:29.429 position:21% line:83% align:start
[LILIA] Lord Claude?
Are you awake in there?

00:05:32.834 --> 00:05:35.036 position:5% line:89% align:start
Stay! And don't utter one peep!

00:05:38.573 --> 00:05:39.607 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LILIA]
Good morning!

00:05:39.740 --> 00:05:41.441 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're looking well today.

00:05:41.576 --> 00:05:42.677 position:30% line:89% align:start
Why, thank you.

00:05:42.810 --> 00:05:44.245 position:24% line:83% align:start
Is there something
that you needed?

00:05:44.377 --> 00:05:46.881 position:19% line:83% align:start
We simply came here to
notify you of a few changes

00:05:47.014 --> 00:05:48.516 position:16% line:89% align:start
to the inspection route.

00:05:48.649 --> 00:05:51.484 position:16% line:83% align:start
And to hand deliver these
cookies I baked for you!

00:05:51.619 --> 00:05:53.386 position:10% line:89% align:start
Would you like to have some?

00:05:54.889 --> 00:05:55.923 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh?

00:05:56.057 --> 00:05:57.592 position:21% line:89% align:start
What's inside there?

00:05:57.725 --> 00:05:59.594 position:24% line:89% align:start
Smells like sweets.

00:05:59.727 --> 00:06:01.662 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yes. That's, uh...

00:06:01.796 --> 00:06:03.396 position:19% line:83% align:start
Just a little something
I had the servants

00:06:03.531 --> 00:06:05.299 position:24% line:83% align:start
throw together in
case I got hungry.

00:06:05.432 --> 00:06:08.536 position:13% line:83% align:start
Aw, so your sweet cravings
are satisfied, too bad.

00:06:08.669 --> 00:06:11.005 position:24% line:83% align:start
What am I supposed
to do with these, then?

00:06:11.138 --> 00:06:14.441 position:24% line:83% align:start
Fear not, for they
won't go to waste.

00:06:14.575 --> 00:06:16.878 position:21% line:83% align:start
Prepare some tea and
we'll eat them right now.

00:06:17.011 --> 00:06:18.179 position:41% line:89% align:start
Lovely!

00:06:19.513 --> 00:06:23.517 position:7% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] He can eat her crusty
cookies but not my apple pie?

00:06:23.651 --> 00:06:26.053 position:27% line:83% align:start
Circling back to
the inspection,

00:06:26.187 --> 00:06:28.322 position:10% line:83% align:start
there's been an unprecedented
amount of demons

00:06:28.455 --> 00:06:29.891 position:24% line:89% align:start
within city limits.

00:06:30.024 --> 00:06:31.259 position:27% line:89% align:start
Demons, you say?

00:06:31.391 --> 00:06:34.161 position:16% line:83% align:start
We shouldn't have issues,
but the knights-in-training

00:06:34.295 --> 00:06:36.030 position:5% line:89% align:start
will be on patrol just in case.

00:06:36.163 --> 00:06:38.933 position:13% line:83% align:start
Only the littlest of demons
have appeared so far.

00:06:41.068 --> 00:06:42.469 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh! I forgot!

00:06:42.603 --> 00:06:45.306 position:10% line:83% align:start
I have an appointment to get
fitted for my inspection dress.

00:06:45.438 --> 00:06:46.674 position:24% line:89% align:start
I should get going.

00:06:46.807 --> 00:06:48.643 position:5% line:89% align:start
CÃ©dric, must you leave, as well?

00:06:48.776 --> 00:06:51.279 position:13% line:89% align:start
No. I can stay for a while.

00:06:51.411 --> 00:06:52.947 position:5% line:89% align:start
Now wait a minute, Lord Claude.

00:06:53.080 --> 00:06:55.983 position:7% line:83% align:start
You've still yet to try one of
my delicious cookies, yes?

00:06:56.117 --> 00:06:58.886 position:19% line:83% align:start
I can't leave until you
at least take a bite.

00:06:59.020 --> 00:07:00.955 position:27% line:89% align:start
Ready? Say "ah."

00:07:03.324 --> 00:07:05.092 position:5% line:89% align:start
This feels highly inappropriate.

00:07:05.226 --> 00:07:08.129 position:10% line:83% align:start
I would hate for your beloved
to get the wrong idea.

00:07:08.262 --> 00:07:09.630 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hush!

00:07:09.764 --> 00:07:10.998 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're my in-law-to-be,
meaning the two of us

00:07:11.132 --> 00:07:12.233 position:30% line:89% align:start
are family now!

00:07:12.366 --> 00:07:15.036 position:19% line:83% align:start
CÃ©dric won't get upset
over something so small.

00:07:15.169 --> 00:07:16.370 position:38% line:89% align:start
Will he?

00:07:16.504 --> 00:07:19.573 position:27% line:83% align:start
Lilia, my brother
is a sensitive man.

00:07:19.707 --> 00:07:20.975 position:24% line:89% align:start
Don't trouble him.

00:07:22.643 --> 00:07:23.644 position:35% line:89% align:start
Understood.

00:07:23.778 --> 00:07:25.346 position:13% line:89% align:start
It was so nice to see you.

00:07:25.478 --> 00:07:27.548 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'll come again soon.

00:07:27.682 --> 00:07:29.050 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
No respect!

00:07:29.183 --> 00:07:30.483 position:19% line:89% align:start
And that cookie stunt?

00:07:30.618 --> 00:07:32.954 position:21% line:83% align:start
With another woman's
fiancÃ©, no less!

00:07:34.322 --> 00:07:35.990 position:13% line:89% align:start
Apologies for her behavior.

00:07:36.123 --> 00:07:38.192 position:24% line:83% align:start
She's grown rather
spoiled lately.

00:07:40.493 --> 00:07:42.263 position:30% line:89% align:start
What? Intruder!

00:07:42.396 --> 00:07:43.864 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Oh, give it a rest.

00:07:43.998 --> 00:07:47.001 position:13% line:83% align:start
Prince CÃ©dric had already
caught on that I was here.

00:07:47.134 --> 00:07:48.235 position:33% line:89% align:start
Is that true?

00:07:48.369 --> 00:07:51.639 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yes, I recognized her
basket almost instantly.

00:07:56.544 --> 00:07:58.079 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'd expect nothing less.

00:07:58.212 --> 00:08:00.982 position:30% line:83% align:start
Lady Lilia's an
excellent baker, yes?

00:08:01.115 --> 00:08:02.950 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yes. Seems so.

00:08:05.419 --> 00:08:06.721 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm leaving. Here.

00:08:06.854 --> 00:08:09.023 position:33% line:83% align:start
More treats?
Why give them to me?

00:08:09.156 --> 00:08:11.726 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well, they're rubbish now,
and rubbish belongs in the bin!

00:08:11.859 --> 00:08:13.861 position:21% line:89% align:start
What's that? The bin?

00:08:13.995 --> 00:08:16.063 position:21% line:83% align:start
You'd dare call your
prince a trash can?

00:08:16.197 --> 00:08:17.164 position:27% line:89% align:start
Just wait, dear.

00:08:17.298 --> 00:08:18.899 position:21% line:83% align:start
Next time, I'll bring
treats so grand,

00:08:19.033 --> 00:08:20.801 position:24% line:83% align:start
these cookies will
seem like kibble!

00:08:20.935 --> 00:08:22.770 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
I'd prefer you didn't!

00:08:24.905 --> 00:08:27.074 position:5% line:89% align:start
See you boys at the inspection!

00:08:30.978 --> 00:08:33.280 position:38% line:83% align:start
Hold on!
You're really planning to come?

00:08:38.719 --> 00:08:40.454 position:38% line:83% align:start
[ELEPHAS]
So, did you find anything out?

00:08:40.588 --> 00:08:44.291 position:10% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] Only that unrequited
love isn't fun for long.

00:08:44.425 --> 00:08:47.094 position:21% line:83% align:start
Pardon my saying so,
but perhaps you should show him

00:08:47.228 --> 00:08:49.096 position:24% line:83% align:start
this more emotional
side of you.

00:08:49.230 --> 00:08:52.099 position:16% line:83% align:start
If there was love between
you, it may awaken it.

00:08:52.233 --> 00:08:53.367 position:47% line:89% align:start
No!

00:08:53.502 --> 00:08:55.836 position:21% line:83% align:start
The last thing I want
is a love born from pity.

00:08:58.439 --> 00:09:00.408 position:38% line:83% align:start
[ALMOND]
Aileen! It's urgent!

00:09:00.541 --> 00:09:02.676 position:21% line:89% align:start
A fight! Come quick!

00:09:05.479 --> 00:09:06.781 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SELENA]
It's mine, give it back!

00:09:06.914 --> 00:09:08.215 position:24% line:89% align:start
No chance in hell!

00:09:08.349 --> 00:09:10.017 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's incense, not some toy!

00:09:10.151 --> 00:09:11.218 position:27% line:89% align:start
You think I care?

00:09:11.352 --> 00:09:12.720 position:13% line:89% align:start
What matters is it's mine!

00:09:12.853 --> 00:09:15.256 position:13% line:83% align:start
Why are you at the capital
in the first place?

00:09:15.389 --> 00:09:17.291 position:19% line:83% align:start
Lord Claude let you go
under one condition!

00:09:17.425 --> 00:09:19.693 position:24% line:83% align:start
That you never step
foot outside Mirchetta!

00:09:19.827 --> 00:09:21.095 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SELENA]
Don't bring up the past!

00:09:21.228 --> 00:09:23.731 position:21% line:83% align:start
This is none of your
business regardless!

00:09:23.864 --> 00:09:25.132 position:24% line:83% align:start
How long have they
been like this?

00:09:25.266 --> 00:09:28.035 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well, approximately since
the moment Auguste

00:09:28.169 --> 00:09:29.937 position:19% line:83% align:start
found her snooping near
the imperial castle

00:09:30.071 --> 00:09:31.972 position:13% line:89% align:start
while he was out on patrol.

00:09:33.174 --> 00:09:35.643 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AUGUSTE]
Ugh! You are so far out of line!

00:09:35.776 --> 00:09:38.145 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
It's been a while, Selena.

00:09:38.279 --> 00:09:41.015 position:24% line:83% align:start
If it isn't Aileen
Lauren d'Autriche.

