00:19:09.917 --> 00:19:11.686 position:38% line:83% align:start
[QUARTZ]
He's bigger than I expected.

00:19:13.988 --> 00:19:15.155 position:30% line:89% align:start
That's my cue.

00:19:15.288 --> 00:19:16.256 position:27% line:83% align:start
Now you want me to
take the demon lord

00:19:16.390 --> 00:19:17.925 position:7% line:89% align:start
and the others to the capital?

00:19:18.059 --> 00:19:19.493 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:19:19.627 --> 00:19:21.095 position:13% line:83% align:start
And to keep up appearances,
tell them the holy knights

00:19:21.228 --> 00:19:23.765 position:10% line:89% align:start
took the demon into custody.

00:19:23.898 --> 00:19:25.833 position:27% line:89% align:start
Always scheming.

00:19:25.967 --> 00:19:28.002 position:5% line:89% align:start
Please, you've seen nothing yet.

00:19:28.136 --> 00:19:31.171 position:13% line:83% align:start
If you don't mind, go ahead
and release Lord Claude.

00:19:45.119 --> 00:19:46.688 position:38% line:89% align:start
My head.

00:19:46.821 --> 00:19:48.856 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ALMOND] Lord Claude!
How we missed you!

00:19:51.159 --> 00:19:53.561 position:33% line:89% align:start
Save my lord!

00:19:55.228 --> 00:19:56.798 position:38% line:89% align:start
No! Stop!

00:19:56.931 --> 00:19:58.099 position:21% line:89% align:start
[DEMON CYCLOPS yells]

00:19:58.231 --> 00:19:59.934 position:10% line:89% align:start
I forbid you to hurt humans!

00:20:00.068 --> 00:20:02.302 position:35% line:89% align:start
Stand down!

00:20:02.436 --> 00:20:06.373 position:7% line:89% align:start
But what about my lord's wish?

00:20:06.507 --> 00:20:08.241 position:30% line:89% align:start
What's my wish?

00:20:09.077 --> 00:20:10.645 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
It's as I thought.

00:20:10.778 --> 00:20:14.048 position:10% line:83% align:start
Distancing myself from Aileen
is of paramount importance.

00:20:14.182 --> 00:20:16.117 position:30% line:89% align:start
You! It's you!

00:20:16.249 --> 00:20:18.820 position:5% line:89% align:start
You're the one in my lord's way!

00:20:18.953 --> 00:20:21.089 position:35% line:89% align:start
Disappear!

00:20:21.221 --> 00:20:23.323 position:19% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] The demons are
intimately connected to Lord

00:20:23.457 --> 00:20:25.693 position:16% line:89% align:start
Claude's heart and mind.

00:20:25.827 --> 00:20:27.962 position:30% line:83% align:start
Does that mean
that his wish is...?

00:20:28.096 --> 00:20:29.296 position:16% line:89% align:start
Disappear from his sight!

00:20:29.429 --> 00:20:31.199 position:41% line:89% align:start
Go now!

00:20:31.331 --> 00:20:33.601 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
...to be rid of me?

00:20:33.735 --> 00:20:35.335 position:38% line:89% align:start
Forever?

00:20:35.469 --> 00:20:37.270 position:30% line:83% align:start
[DEMON CYCLOPS]
Disappear!

00:20:37.404 --> 00:20:38.740 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AUGUSTE]
Ailey! Look out!

00:20:38.873 --> 00:20:41.976 position:27% line:83% align:start
Hey, Walt! Kyle!
Ready your guns!

00:20:42.110 --> 00:20:43.978 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Don't kill him!

00:20:44.112 --> 00:20:45.312 position:21% line:89% align:start
Think of Lord Claude.

00:20:45.445 --> 00:20:46.681 position:21% line:89% align:start
He would be crushed.

00:20:46.814 --> 00:20:48.750 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yells]

00:21:02.262 --> 00:21:03.798 position:35% line:89% align:start
Poor fool.

00:21:03.931 --> 00:21:09.003 position:13% line:83% align:start
His fragile state made him
misunderstand my lord's wish.

00:21:09.137 --> 00:21:10.470 position:44% line:89% align:start
Sir.

00:21:10.605 --> 00:21:13.775 position:16% line:83% align:start
We strive to follow your
orders as best we can.

00:21:13.908 --> 00:21:20.047 position:7% line:83% align:start
As such, if you order us away,
then away we shall go.

00:21:30.191 --> 00:21:31.626 position:30% line:89% align:start
My Lord Claude.

00:21:31.759 --> 00:21:34.028 position:19% line:83% align:start
Seems I must be on your
mind all hours of the day,

00:21:34.162 --> 00:21:37.765 position:16% line:83% align:start
if ridding yourself of me
is your greatest desire.

00:21:37.899 --> 00:21:41.368 position:24% line:83% align:start
Now, flash a smile.
You're a pro these days.

00:21:45.305 --> 00:21:50.178 position:7% line:83% align:start
First rule of unrequited love:
Set your expectations at zero.

00:21:50.310 --> 00:21:51.579 position:33% line:89% align:start
But still...

00:22:03.157 --> 00:22:06.828 position:19% line:83% align:start
If I am so in your way,
then I shall be gone as well!

00:22:06.961 --> 00:22:09.797 position:13% line:83% align:start
And rest assured, you will
not see me at the ball!

